OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FParents in Dumfries and Galloway are
OL,8,Fcalling on the council to carefully
OL,9,Fconsider it's decision on the future
OL,10,Fof five nurseries.
OL,12,FLast week parents were contacted to
OL,13,Fsay nursery provision would be paused
OL,14,Fat schools in Collin, Creetown,
OL,15,FDrummore, Kirkowan and Dumfries.
OL,17,FThe council said nursery aged children
OL,18,Fattending these settings should be
OL,19,Fenrolled at different schools, due to
OL,20,Fprojections of fewer than 10 children
OL,21,Fat each site.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FHowever, on Friday, the authority
OL,8,Fapologised and announced the plans
OL,9,Fwill now go to consultation before any
OL,10,Fclosures were confirmed.
OL,12,FBut parents say they have been left
OL,13,F"terrified" that the provision they
OL,14,Fhave grown to rely on will be taken
OL,15,Ffrom them following that process.
OL,17,FErika Jermyn moved from Lincolnshire
OL,18,Fto a village near Creetown with her
OL,19,Fhusband Rob and their two children,
OL,20,FDuncan and Tom, in 2018.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FIn 2024, following a cancer diagnosis,
OL,8,FRob died and Erika was left looking
OL,9,Fafter her two very young children on
OL,10,Fher own in an area that she was still
OL,11,Frelatively new to.
OL,13,FErika works in antiques and she says
OL,14,Fshe had to rely on the nursery so that
OL,15,Fshe could continue working to earn a
OL,16,Fliving following her husband's death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FShe says although she considered
OL,8,Fmoving back down south to be closer to
OL,9,Fher family, the support she received
OL,10,Ffrom the nursery and the community
OL,11,Fplayed a huge part in her decision to
OL,12,Fstay.
OL,14,FErika said the potential closures came
OL,15,Fwith "no warning" and she felt
OL,16,F"shocked, scared and worried" when she
OL,17,Ffirst heard the news.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FErika said: "Duncan was only 18 months
OL,8,Fold when his dad passed and he
OL,9,Fobviously didn't understand where his
OL,10,Fdad went. And it did affect him quite
OL,11,Fbadly. Really bad night time
OL,12,Fnightmares, screaming for his dad. He
OL,13,Fwas very, very clingy towards me. I
OL,14,Fcouldn't leave the room without him
OL,15,Fwanting to come with me.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,F"As a self-employed mum, I had to
OL,8,Fcarry on working. So as soon as he
OL,9,Fturned two, he joined nursery. And
OL,10,Fthey know me. Everyone, all the
OL,11,Fteachers know me. They know what I've
OL,12,Fbeen through, what's happened, what
OL,13,Fthese two have been through.
OL,15,F"And they helped. They helped
OL,16,Fimmensely. So they were my lifeline
OL,17,Fbasically."
OL,19,FIt's a feeling that is echoed by many
OL,20,Fpeople who send their children to the
OL,21,Fsame nursery.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FAt the school gates today one parent
OL,8,Fsaid: "I think they've realised that
OL,9,Fthey made a monumental mistake when it
OL,10,Fcomes to trying to phone parents and
OL,11,Fjust ask them if they're willing to
OL,12,Fsend kids anywhere else."
OL,14,F"I was upset," said another parent.
OL,15,F"My other two children go here and if
OL,16,Fthe nursery shuts there's no way I'm
OL,17,Fgoing to get them there and get the
OL,18,Fother daughter to Newton Stewart - and
OL,19,FI don't drive so I've got no way of
OL,20,Fdoing it!"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FAnother said: "The way it was handled
OL,8,Fwas not right. It's very short sighted
OL,9,Fas well because if they're talking
OL,10,Fabout wanting families with young
OL,11,Fchildren to move into the area, that's
OL,12,Fnot going to encourage them if there's
OL,13,Fno nursery for the little ones for
OL,14,Fworking parents, not ideal.
OL,16,F"The whole way it was handled it just
OL,17,Fcaused so much stress and upset," she
OL,18,Fadded.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FThe Conservative MSP for Galloway and
OL,8,FWest Dumfries, Finlay Carson, says
OL,9,Fschools and nurseries play a critical
OL,10,Frole in maintaining rural populations
OL,11,Fand potential.
OL,13,FHe says that if education settings are
OL,14,Ftaken away from these areas then there
OL,15,Fis less incentive for people to move
OL,16,Fthere, resulting in rural decline.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border, he said: "The
OL,8,Fcouncil themselves just published a
OL,9,Freport about rural depopulation and at
OL,10,Fthe core of that was how damaging the
OL,11,Fremoval of some services from villages
OL,12,Fcan be. There's a domino effect.
OL,14,F"So to announce the closure of these
OL,15,Fnurseries without doing any
OL,16,Fconsultation, without looking at the
OL,17,Fconsequences of closing a nursery, is
OL,18,Fcompletely unacceptable."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FOn Friday, Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,Fcouncil apologised for "confusion and
OL,9,Fupset" caused by communications around
OL,10,Fnursery provision at the five small
OL,11,Fnurseries in the region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FCllr Tracey Little, Chair of Dumfries
OL,8,Fand Galloway Council's Education,
OL,9,FSkills and Community Wellbeing
OL,10,Fcommittee, said: "Following the recent
OL,11,Fnursery enrolment process, six council-
OL,12,Frun nurseries were identified as
OL,13,Fhaving projected rolls of fewer than
OL,14,F10 children. In response, the council
OL,15,Fmoved to pause provision at five
OL,16,Fnursery settings from August 2026 and
OL,17,Foffer families alternative places at
OL,18,Fnearby nurseries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,F"Although this action was taken in
OL,8,Fgood faith and is consistent with
OL,9,FScottish Government guidance on
OL,10,Ftemporary closures, we now acknowledge
OL,11,Fthat it does not reflect the
OL,12,Fexpectation that was set by what was
OL,13,Fpresented to the public and elected
OL,14,Fmembers at Full Council on 26 February
OL,15,F2026.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,F"The agreed position, as set out in
OL,8,Fthe 2026/27 budget, was to undertake
OL,9,Fstatutory consultation on the future
OL,10,Fof very small council-run nurseries
OL,11,Fwith low enrolment. That consultation
OL,12,Fhas not yet taken place.
OL,14,F"We have reviewed our approach to
OL,15,Fensure it aligns with the democratic
OL,16,Fdecision taken by elected members and
OL,17,Fthe expectations of our communities.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,F"No final decisions have been made
OL,8,Fabout the long-term future of any
OL,9,Fnursery setting and plans to
OL,10,Ftemporarily close the five nursery
OL,11,Fsettings will now not go ahead.
OL,13,F"Going forward, the council will
OL,14,Fundertake formal statutory
OL,15,Fconsultation on the future of each of
OL,16,Fthe five nursery settings. The outcome
OL,17,Fof the statutory consultation process
OL,18,Fwill inform the council's next steps."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FIt added that that council is
OL,8,Fcommitted to working to ensure that
OL,9,Fevery nursery and school is the right
OL,10,Fsize, in the right location, and able
OL,11,Fto deliver the best possible learning
OL,12,Fexperiences for children and young
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,FBut Erika says the nursery that
OL,16,Fsupported her family is more than just
OL,17,Fa learning environment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773688273
OL,3,C'Scared and worried': Parents urge
OL,4,Ccouncil not to close 'lifeline'
OL,5,Cnurseries
OL,7,FShe said: "I need to tell my story so
OL,8,Fthat these councillors know that our
OL,9,Frural schools are not just a place for
OL,10,Four children to get an education, but
OL,11,Fto receive a personal experience from
OL,12,Fthe amazing teachers who support us
OL,13,Ffamilies and communities."
OL,15,FShe says she wants to "show others
OL,16,Fthat if you stick together, it can
OL,17,Fmake you stronger."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
